<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html>
<head> 
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Geo-Memories</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="Jogging_App_StyleSheet.css">
    <script src="Jogging_App_JS.js" defer></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div>
            <div class = "mapDiv" id="mapDiv" style="width: 100%; height: 800px"></div>
            <div id="floatingPanel">
                <button class = "hover-button" id="center">Center</button> 
                <button class = "hover-button" id="delAll">Delete All</button>
            </div>
            <div id="form-box">
                <div id="box">
                    <div id="form">
                        <div>
                            <form>
                                <b>Create a GeoMemory</b><br>
                                <label for="title">Title:</label>
                                <input type="text" id="title"><br>
                                <label for="text-content">Message:</label>
                                <input type="text" id="text-content"><br>
                                <label for="checkbox">Use marker coordinates</label>
                                <input type="checkbox" id="marker-coords"><br>
                                <input type="file" id="file-input" accept="image/png, image/jpg">
                            </form>
                            <div id="buttonHolder">
                                <button class="button" id="submitMemory">Submit Memory</button>
                                <button class="button" id="editMemory">Apply Edits</button>
                            </div>
                            
                        </div>
                        <div id="display-image">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="instructions">
                        <p>
                            <b>Instructions</b><br>
                                - The red marker is for creating a GeoMemory at a location other than your current location. <br>
                                - It can be dragged around by holding and moving the cursor. Upon letting go it will be placed at the position.<br>
                                - To use the coordinates of the red marker for a GeoMemory check the checkbox<br>
                                - The blue marker represents your location (on startup, the red marker may be covering the blue marker)<br>
                                - To add an image, click on choose file and select an image (These can only be in .png and .jpg file formats)<br>
                                - The image will appear in the preview box and then will be added to the GeoMemory upon submitting<br>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="geoMList">
                    <td><label id="geom-postbox-title"><h2>Geo Memories</h2></label></td>
                    <td>
                        <div id="flexContainer"></div>
                    </td>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyAEmGm-PIIFijbgz06Zem6kyoH9HOxJQFM&callback=initMap&v=weekly" defer>
        </script>
    </body>
</html> 